<PageLayout title="Mekanisme Permohonan Informasi - PPID SMKN 14 Jakarta">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-8xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Dokumen Terkait - Paling Atas -->
      <div class="mb-12 bg-indigo-50 rounded-lg p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <file-text class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600 mr-3" />
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-800">Dokumen Terkait Mekanisme Permohonan Informasi</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-indigo-700 mb-6">
          <strong>Penting:</strong> Silakan lihat dokumen PDF terlebih dahulu untuk memahami mekanisme permohonan informasi secara detail.
          Dokumen dapat dilihat langsung di browser atau diunduh untuk referensi offline.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- PDF Viewer Section -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Lihat Dokumen PDF</h3>
            <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
              <iframe id="pdf-viewer" src="/StandarLayanan/Mekanisme Permohonan Informasi (2).pdf" class="w-full h-[1000px]" frameborder="0"></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 flex justify-end">
              <a id="download-button" href="/StandarLayanan/Mekanisme Permohonan Informasi (2).pdf" download="Mekanisme Permohonan Informasi.pdf" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors shadow-md">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"></path></svg>
                Unduh PDF
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Document Selection Section -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Pilih Dokumen untuk Dilihat</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <button data-src="/StandarLayanan/Mekanisme Permohonan Informasi (2).pdf" class="document-button flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-indigo-100 hover:bg-indigo-200 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path></svg>
                  <span class="text-indigo-800 font-medium">Mekanisme Permohonan Informasi.pdf</span>
                </div>
              </button>
              <button data-src="/StandarLayanan/11b.-SOP-PENGELOLAAN-PERMOHONAN-INFORMASI-PUBLIK-2024.pdf" class="document-button flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-green-100 hover:bg-green-200 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path></svg>
                  <span class="text-green-800 font-medium">SOP Pengelolaan Permohonan Informasi Publik 2024.pdf</span>
                </div>
              </button>
              <button data-src="/StandarLayanan/11b.-SOP-PENGELOLAAN-PERMOHONAN-INFORMASI-PUBLIK-2025.pdf" class="document-button flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-blue-100 hover:bg-blue-200 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path></svg>
                  <span class="text-blue-800 font-medium">SOP Pengelolaan Permohonan Informasi Publik 2025.pdf</span>
                </div>
              </button>
              <button data-src="/StandarLayanan/FORMULIR-PERMINTAAN-INFORMASI-PUBLIK-2025.pdf" class="document-button flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-purple-100 hover:bg-purple-200 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path></svg>
                  <span class="text-purple-800 font-medium">Formulir Permintaan Informasi Publik 2025.pdf</span>
                </div>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">
        Mekanisme Permohonan Informasi
      </h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Mekanisme permohonan informasi publik di PPID SMKN 14 Jakarta
          dirancang untuk memudahkan masyarakat dalam mengakses informasi sesuai
          dengan prinsip transparansi dan akuntabilitas pemerintahan.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">
          Jenis Mekanisme Permohonan
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 rounded-lg p-6"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-blue-500 rounded-full p-2 mr-3">
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-white"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-800">Tertulis</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>Surat permohonan resmi</li>
              <li>Formulir permohonan PPID</li>
              <li>Email dengan tanda tangan digital</li>
              <li>Faksimile dengan identitas</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 rounded-lg p-6"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-green-500 rounded-full p-2 mr-3">
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-white"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-800">Lisan</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>Konsultasi langsung di kantor PPID</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">
          Mekanisme Online
        </h2>
        <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-800 mb-4">
            Sistem Informasi PPID Online
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div
                class="bg-indigo-500 rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-1"
              >
                <span class="text-white font-bold">1</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                  Registrasi Akun
                </h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  Pemohon membuat akun di sistem PPID online dengan email aktif
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div
                class="bg-indigo-500 rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-1"
              >
                <span class="text-white font-bold">2</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                  Pengisian Formulir
                </h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  Pemohon mengisi formulir permohonan secara digital dengan
                  lengkap
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div
                class="bg-indigo-500 rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-1"
              >
                <span class="text-white font-bold">3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Upload Dokumen</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  Upload scan identitas dan dokumen pendukung yang diperlukan
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div
                class="bg-indigo-500 rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-1"
              >
                <span class="text-white font-bold">4</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                  Submit dan Tracking
                </h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  Submit permohonan dan dapatkan nomor tracking untuk monitoring
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">
          Mekanisme Offline
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
              Datang Langsung
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Lokasi:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  Ruang PPID SMKN 14 Jakarta<br />Jl. Percetakan Negara IIA
                  No.2, Johar Baru, Jakarta Pusat
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Jam Pelayanan:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  Senin - Jumat: 06:30 - 15:00 WIB
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Kontak:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  Telepon: (021) 4240543<br />Email: smkn14jakarta@gmail.com
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const viewer = document.getElementById('pdf-viewer') as HTMLIFrameElement;
    const downloadButton = document.getElementById('download-button') as HTMLAnchorElement;
    const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('.document-button');

    buttons.forEach(button => {
      button.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const src = button.getAttribute('data-src');
        if (src) {
          viewer.src = src;
          downloadButton.href = src;
          const fileName = src.split('/').pop() || 'document.pdf';
          downloadButton.download = fileName;
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>
